import React from 'react' import { difficultyLevels, durationLevels } from './ActivitiesLevels' import style from './ActivityCard.module.css' export default function ActivityCard({ name, difficulty, duration, season }) { return (

{name}

Dif: {difficultyLevels[difficulty - 1]}
Dur: {durationLevels[duration - 1]}
Sea: {season}

) }
